  "description": [
    "Annual Scientific Assembly Will Be Held Wednesday and Thursday The annual scientific assembly of the Medical Society of the District will be held Wednesday and Thurs day at the societys building with a distinguished list of medical papers to be presented Besides the scientific sessions there will be a public meeting Wednesday night addressed bv Dr George Bur gess Magrath professor of legal medi cine at Harvard University The an nual banquet will be held at the Mayflower Hotel Thursday evening A luncheon will be held at the May flower Wednesday noon at the same time as the annual luncheon of the Womens Auxiliary Papers Will Be Head At the Wednesday morning session the following papers will be presented Xray diagnosis of small bowel pathology Dr Joseph F Elward as sociate professor of roentgenology Georgetown University hyperpara thyrodism Dr James A Cahill pro fessor of surgery at Georgetown peripgeral neuritis Dr Walter Free man professor of neurology George Washington University bronchoscopy in suppurative and malignant dis eases of the lung Dr David Davis associate in otolargology George Washington evipan anesthesia Dr Charles Stanley White professor of surgery George Washington the prostrate gland in middle life Dr Alan J Chenery associate"
